---
layout: base
title: Articles
description: Practical language-learning activities and frameworks.
permalink: /articles/
---

<h1>Articles</h1>
<p class="lede">Practical language-learning activities and frameworks you can use with any language.</p>

<div class="post-list">
  {%- for item in collections.articles -%}
    <article class="post-item">
      <h2 class="post-title">
        <a href="{{ item.url }}">{{ item.data.title }}</a>
      </h2>

      <p class="post-meta">
        <span class="post-date">{{ item.date | readableDate }}</span>
        {%- if item.data.summary -%}
          <span class="post-dot">-</span>
          <span class="post-summary">{{ item.data.summary }}</span>
        {%- endif -%}
      </p>

      {%- if item.data.excerpt -%}
        <p class="post-summary">{{ item.data.excerpt | safe }}</p>
      {%- endif -%}

      <p class="post-readmore">
        <a href="{{ item.url }}">Read -></a>
      </p>
    </article>
  {%- endfor -%}
</div>
